snippet: Manchester United remain very dangerous opponents despite their struggles domestically as they focus their efforts on Europe, Bayern Munich coach Pep Guardiola said on the eve of their Champions League quarter-final first leg....

headline.print_headline: Guardiola Fears United's Best Two Displays of the Season
headline.main: Guardiola Fears United's Best Two Displays of the Season

lead_paragraph: Manchester United remain very dangerous opponents despite their struggles domestically as they focus their efforts on Europe, Bayern Munich coach Pep Guardiola said on the eve of their Champions League quarter-final first leg.
